Package: oncofix
Version: 1.0.0
Section: healthcare
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 18.0.0), python3 (>= 3.8), python3-venv, nginx, sqlite3, rabbitmq-server, erlang-base
Recommends: pm2
Maintainer: OncoFix Team <support@oncofix.com>
Description: OncoFix - Oral Cancer Screening Platform
 OncoFix is an offline-first healthcare application for oral cancer
 screening on OrangePi5 devices.
 .
 Components:
  - NestJS backend API (port 443)
  - React frontend SPA (port 8082 via Nginx)
  - MONAI AI cancer prediction model
  - RabbitMQ-based sync to Google BigQuery
 .
 Default device ID: OPi5_oncofix_default_001
